longBusinessSummary: iMining Blockchain and Cryptocurrency Inc., a blockchain and cryptocurrency company, engages in cryptocurrency mining business. The company is involved in deploying, managing validators, holding, or investing in crypto currencies. It serves corporate, financial institutions, and private investors. The company was formerly known as Parlane Resource Corp. and changed its name to iMining Blockchain and Cryptocurrency Inc. in April 2018. iMining Blockchain and Cryptocurrency Inc. was incorporated in 2007 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
